name: Honey 2D
description:
Cause water doesn't come this THICC!

You want thicc thighs, wide hips, gloooorious squishes all around? Your squishes to be mouth watering like a freshly opened tube of biscuits? So does this model!!

As shown in the nurse pics above, a couple parenthesis can go a loooong way!

This model is meant to produce what I find to be the most screen-grabbing 2D I could possibly manage at the moment, so it'll take some time and lots of testing for me to update it.

NSFW promo images are in the gallery below.

There is no baked in VAE.
The VAE I use: Grapefruit VAE

As like my other models, my usual settings:

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras
Sample Steps: 20-35
Upscaler: ESRGAN_4x
Deniose: 0.5
CFG: 5-9

By no means is this law, feel free to experiment and I'd love to see your results!!

For inpainting, you can use whatever res you'd like! There's no realism models present, so it won't get overly-detailed at 800+ res like my semi-realism models. You shouldn't need to change your prompt at all when inpainting faces to get a good result. This is always a goal of mine, as I prefer not to have to do any extra steps in my workflow if possible.

All images above were inpainted using the same prompt I used to make the image.
